0px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: #181818; font-family: open-sans, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.8px;\\\">With its tall towers and famous trademarked \\\"international orange\\\" paint job, the bridge quickly became a famous American landmark, and a symbol of San Francisco.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
